

### 项目结构

```
├── README.md
├── config
│   └── config.go
├── debug.sh
├── discover
│   ├── discover.go
│   └── kit.go
├── endpoint
│   ├── discover.go
│   ├── endpoint.go
│   ├── health_check.go
│   └── ping_pong.go
├── server.go
├── service
│   ├── discover.go
│   ├── error.go
│   └── service.go
└── transport
    └── transport.go
```

1) config 配置
2) discover 服务注册与发现
3) endpoint 接收请求与响应
4) service 业务逻辑层
5) transport 提供HTTP服务





### 本地搭建和测试

```shell

```

##### 启动
```shell
consul agent -dev
```

```shell
http://localhost:8500
```

##### 接口测试

```json
http://127.0.0.1:8030/ping
http://127.0.0.1:8030/health
http://127.0.0.1:8030/discovery?serviceName=micro_in_action
```
